snippet.title: Genshin Impact Official Fontaine Gameplay
snippet.description:
Check out gameplay from the upcoming new region, Fontaine, arriving in Genshin Impact's Version 4.0. Featuring plenty of new characters to meet and stories to discover, plus the ability to explore underwater for the first time, the open-world action-RPG is about to get even bigger.

#IGN
